<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Paiement automatique effectué</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f5; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #18181b; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 580px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
    .header { background: #18181b; padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header .logo { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #facc15; letter-spacing: -1px; }
    .header .logo span { color: #ffffff; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .body h1 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .body p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #52525b; margin: 0 0 20px; }
    .check-icon { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .check-icon svg { width: 56px; height: 56px; }
    .summary { border: 1px solid #e4e4e7; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .summary-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f4f4f5; font-size: 14px; }
    .summary-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .summary-row .label { color: #71717a; }
    .summary-row .value { font-weight: 600; color: #18181b; }
    .amount-row { background: #f0fdf4; }
    .amount-row .value { color: #15803d; font-size: 18px; }
    .footer { background: #f4f4f5; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #a1a1aa; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo"><span>Lvl</span>Up</div>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <div class="check-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 56 56" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="28" cy="28" r="28" fill="#dcfce7"/>
          <path d="M18 28.5L24.5 35L38 21" stroke="#15803d" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1>Paiement automatique effectué</h1>
      <p>Bonjour {{ profile.firstName }},</p>
      <p>Votre paiement automatique a été <strong>traité avec succès</strong>. Voici le récapitulatif de l'opération :</p>
      <div class="summary">
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span class="label">Référence paiement</span>
          <span class="value">{{ payment.id|slice(0, 8)|upper }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span class="label">Profil</span>
          <span class="value">{{ profile.firstName }} {{ profile.lastName }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span class="label">Méthode</span>
          <span class="value">{{ payment.method.value }}</span>
        </div>
        {% if payment.paidAt %}
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span class="label">Date du prélèvement</span>
          <span class="value">{{ payment.paidAt|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}</span>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="summary-row amount-row">
          <span class="label"><strong>Montant prélevé</strong></span>
          <span class="value">{{ (payment.amount / 100)|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>Si vous avez des questions concernant ce prélèvement, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter.</p>
      <p>Merci de votre confiance !</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} LvlUp &mdash; Tous droits réservés.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
